        "ellipsisCount": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 2,
      "text": "The advantage of this persuasion is, that it fixes the attention of the young man on the most eligible matches, thereby facilitating the natural course of courtship and matrimonial alliance.",
      "startTime": 23.233,
      "endTime": 35.031,
      "duration": 11.798,
